593
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,590
Li Shuang of the Changfeng Army

594
00:34:51,590 --> 00:34:54,050
requests an audience
with the Crown Prince.

595
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:05,490
Greetings, Your Highness.

596
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:08,110
Please rise.

597
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,730
There are no outsiders here.

598
00:35:09,730 --> 00:35:11,390
No need for such formalities.

599
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,550
Shuang,

600
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,150
what brings you here?

601
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,440
Your Highness has not fully recovered

602
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,920
but personally rewarded the army.

603
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,970
It's truly a blessing
for the Changfeng Army.

604
00:35:30,970 --> 00:35:32,820
I must thank you in person.

605
00:35:35,740 --> 00:35:36,590
Also, this...

606
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,360
It's the finest wound salve,

607
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:41,120
a gift from a renowned
physician friend of mine.

608
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:43,050
It works wonders for sword wounds.

609
00:35:49,720 --> 00:35:51,580
No wonder you're distant with me.

610
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:53,260
I've missed so much

611
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,630
of your life.

612
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,710
Three years have passed in a flash.

613
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,920
Here at the border,

614
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,680
you've made new friends.

615
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:03,920
I'm glad you have.

616
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:08,800
Her name is Lu Xin.

617
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,760
She saved me when I was injured.

618
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:12,180
She's a close friend

619
00:36:12,180 --> 00:36:13,110
to whom I'm indebted.

620
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,170
If you're willing,

621
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:16,510
tell me more, will you?

622
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,400
I've been fine

623
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,370
these 3 years at the border.

624
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,400
Besides Lu Xin,

625
00:36:23,710 --> 00:36:25,110
I've made another friend

626
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,300
called Jin'an.

627
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:32,260
Though I found him and took him in,

628
00:36:32,630 --> 00:36:34,690
he's saved me many times from danger.

629
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:37,360
He didn't mean
to offend Your Highness earlier.

630
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,320
I'm willing

631
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:41,010
to accept any punishment for him.

632
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:46,320
I've never cared much for etiquette.

633
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,830
Why would I hold it against him?

634
00:36:47,830 --> 00:36:49,960
The more trustworthy
the people by your side,

635
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,320
the more at ease I can be.

636
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:54,260
Thank you for your understanding.

637
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:56,030
You haven't fully recovered yet.

638
00:36:56,030 --> 00:36:58,160
You should head back and get some rest.

639
00:36:58,360 --> 00:37:00,760
I still have
military matters to attend to.

640
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,100
I'll take my leave now.

641
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:13,470
Your Highness, it seems
General Li still cares about you.

642
00:37:13,470 --> 00:37:17,130
Otherwise, she wouldn't have
come in person to give you the salve.

643
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:19,480
I'll certainly

644
00:37:20,150 --> 00:37:21,670
be nice to her friends.

645
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,200
But seeing her so careful with me

646
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:28,110
makes me really sad.

647
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:32,330
Have you investigated

648
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,720
Jin'an's identity?

649
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,440
There's little information about him.

650
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,670
Nothing seems suspicious.

651
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:39,360
It's said that when General Li found him,

652
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:41,910
he had already suffered a head injury
and lost his memory.

653
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:42,500
Besides,

654
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:43,840
he was the one who killed Huo Du.